data.description: This extremely spacious ''fixer-upper'' boast 2736 sq ft of living area and a detached structure that consists of a workshop and an outdoor kitchen.  The home features 4 spacious bedrooms and 2 bathrooms all with plenty of storage space.  The kitchen is well planned and connects to the dining area.  The family room is huge and can serve as several different sitting areas.  Just off of the family room is a glassed-in patio with even more storage space.
